.    A             B
 And carried all my grief; ||
.   C#m     B         A     E
 His hand a thousand blessings pours,
.    C#m    B       A
 Upon my guilty head,
.      A      B      A
 His presence gilds my darkest hours,
.    B               E
 And guards my sleeping bed.
 
[V4]
.   E                   B
