.    A             B
 And saves me from the grave; ||
.   C#m     B         A     E
 To Heaven the place of His abode,
.    C#m    B       A
 He brings my weary feet,
.      A      B      A
 Shows me the glories of my God
.    B               E
 And makes my joy complete.
 
[V5]
